### Bulk Scheduling Test - Tiffin Management System
### First login to get access token

# Login as demo user
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@tiffin.com",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### Copy the accessToken from above response and use it in Authorization header below

### 1. Create bulk meals for specific dates array
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "dates": ["2024-01-15", "2024-01-16", "2024-01-17"],
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Bulk scheduled lunch"
}

### 2. Create bulk meals for date range (all days)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-20",
  "endDate": "2024-01-25",
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Week breakfast schedule"
}

### 3. Create bulk meals for date range (skip weekends)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-22",
  "endDate": "2024-01-28",
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "count": 2,
  "skipWeekends": true,
  "note": "Weekday dinners only"
}

### 4. Create bulk meals for specific days of week (Monday to Friday)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-02-01",
  "endDate": "2024-02-15",
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 1,
  "daysOfWeek": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
  "note": "Workday lunches"
}

### 5. List all meals to see bulk scheduled ones
GET http://localhost:3003/meals
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. List meals in date range
GET http://localhost:3003/meals?startDate=2024-01-15&endDate=2024-02-15
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Get calendar view for January 2024
GET http://localhost:3003/meals/calendar?month=2024-01
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Bulk update meals in date range
PATCH http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "endDate": "2024-01-17",
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 2,
  "note": "Updated to 2 servings"
}

### 9. Bulk cancel meals in date range
DELETE http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-20",
  "endDate": "2024-01-25",
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST"
}

### 10. Check dashboard to see totals
GET http://localhost:3003/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE